    section.main-content
        article.intro.mb-5
            .intro-content.reverse-container.flex-wrap.pr-md-0
                p.subheading Intro
                p.heading.intro-heading Our future
                p.lead.intro-lead Apparently we had reached a great height in the atmosphere, for the sky
                    | was a dead black, and the stars had ceased to twinkle.
                p.text-content By the same illusion which lifts the horizon of the sea to the level of the
                    | spectator on a hillside, the sable cloud beneath was dished out, and the car seemed
                    | to float in the middle of an immense dark sphere, whose upper half was strewn with silver.
                a.button-main(href="#") Learn more
            .intro-img-block.reverse-container.px-md-0
                .img-thumb
                    img.article--img(src='../img/intro-img.png')
                .quote
                    .blockquote--block-big.d-none.d-sm-block
                    .blockquote--block
                        p Commodo sed egestas egestas fringilla phasellus faucibus.

        article.features
            .bg-container.d-md-block.d-none
            .features-wrapper
                .container
                    p.features-subheading Benefits
                    .row
                        .col-md-5.features-content
                            p.heading.features-heading Shaping the future
                            p.lead.features-lead Eget nunc scelerisque viverra mauris in aliquam. Dignissim sodales ut
                                | eu sem integer vitae. Libero nunc consequat interdum varius.
                            p.text-content.features-text-content Magna sit amet purus gravida. Sit amet porttitor eget dolor morbi non.
                                | Lectus vestibulum mattis ullamcorper velit sed ullamcorper.
                                | Diam phasellus vestibulum lorem sed risus ultricies tristique nulla. Dui faucibus
                                | in ornare quam viverra.
                                | Posuere ac ut consequat semper viverra.
                            a.button-main(href="#") Learn more
                        .col-md-5.offset-md-1.offset-0.col-sm-12
                            .row
                            img.article--img.img-fluid(src='../img/feature-img.png')
                        .col-md-1.d-md-flex.d-none
                            a(href="#" target="_blank").app-link Mobile App
                    .row
                        .col-md-2.offset-md-9
                            .pager
                                .counter.d-none.d-md-block
                                    span.current 1
                                    span /
                                    span.total 3
                                .controls
                                    button(type="button").left.mr-3.mr-md-0
                                        svg.arrow-right-short.arrow-right--reverse(width="27" height="27" fill="none")
                                            circle(cx="13.5" cy="13.5" r="13" stroke="#F61067" stroke-opacity=".5")
